(756, 1, '2015-02-16 14:49:21', '2015-02-16 14:49:21', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][trx_section bg_tint=\"light\" class=\"accent_top\" animation=\"fadeInUp\" dedicated=\"\" align=\"none\" columns=\"none\" pan=\"\" scroll=\"\" scroll_dir=\"horizontal\" scroll_controls=\"horizontal\" font_weight=\"inherit\" top=\"80\" bottom=\"120\"][trx_content animation=\"none\"][trx_title type=\"2\" style=\"regular\" align=\"center\" top=\"0\" bottom=\"0.85em\"]Why Our Barbershop?[/trx_title][trx_columns count=\"2\"][trx_column_item][trx_block][trx_icon icon=\"icon-male184\" font_size=\"4.5em\" align=\"left\" bottom=\"0.15em\" right=\"0.5em\" class=\"link_color\" bg_shape=\"none\" bg_style=\"custom\" font_weight=\"inherit\"][vc_column_text]Our barbershop is the territory created purely for males who value premium quality, time and flawless look. You will get a cut of your life and spend great time with your buddies.[/vc_column_text][/trx_block][trx_block top=\"0.5em\"][trx_icon icon=\"icon-razor1\" font_size=\"4.5em\" align=\"left\" bottom=\"0.15em\" right=\"0.5em\" class=\"link_color\" bg_shape=\"none\" bg_style=\"custom\" font_weight=\"inherit\"][vc_column_text]Our services spectrum encompasses many techniques and procedures – from straight razor shaving and hairstyling to beard care and eyebrow grooming. Whether you just need a quick touch, or the whole pack - we\'ll do that for you![/vc_column_text][/trx_block][trx_block top=\"1.5em\"][trx_icon icon=\"icon-male185\" font_size=\"4.5em\" align=\"left\" bottom=\"0.15em\" right=\"0.5em\" class=\"link_color\" bg_shape=\"none\" bg_style=\"custom\" font_weight=\"inherit\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our barbershop means a relaxed and easy atmosphere, and always a top quality service for men! Come in and enjoy the conversation and the best haircut you’ve ever had.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/trx_block][/trx_column_item][trx_column_item][trx_video url=\"https://vimeo.com/116429405\" height=\"335\" autoplay=\"off